OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FA woman from Talbot Green says she was
OL,8,Fleft traumatised after watching her
OL,9,Ffather die without enough support
OL,10,Fbecause of a "lack of" palliative care.
OL,12,FClare Williams' dad Paul Jones was
OL,13,Fgiven a terminal diagnosis for bowel
OL,14,Fcancer in August 2015 and died a year
OL,15,Flater. He wanted to be at home to die
OL,16,Fbut Clare says the support for him to
OL,17,Fdo so wasn't good enough.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FIt comes as the charity Marie Curie
OL,8,Fsays the system in Wales "is broken",
OL,9,Fwith almost one in three adults having
OL,10,Ftheir palliative care needs unmet.
OL,12,FReflecting on her father's experience,
OL,13,FClare said: "I feel like we were
OL,14,Ffailed when I look back at it. At the
OL,15,Ftime you're immersed in it and you
OL,16,Fdon't really realise and now I think
OL,17,Fabout it, unless we asked for things
OL,18,For chased people then you weren't
OL,19,Foffered (help).
OL,26,@{D@Ipm{D@Npn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"The community nursing team were
OL,8,Finvolved, they would come to see my
OL,9,Fdad at the house but that wasn't very
OL,10,Foften and during the last week (of his
OL,11,Flife) they came in approximately once.
OL,13,F"He was unconscious for a week and we
OL,14,Fsaw them once.
OL,16,F"The last day he was alive, he was
OL,17,Fmaking a wailing noise and we phoned
OL,18,Fthem and it took hours for them to
OL,19,Fcome and we didn't understand what was
OL,20,Fgoing on, we had no preparation.
OL,26,@rD@`pmsD@Epn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"We weren't prepared for what death
OL,8,Fwould look like, people don't talk
OL,9,Fabout what death is going to look
OL,10,Flike, this is a taboo subject so we
OL,11,Fweren't prepared for what he could go
OL,12,Fthrough, what noises he could make,
OL,13,Fwhat could happen. We had absolutely
OL,14,Fno idea.
OL,16,F"There (were) no check-ins, 'do you
OL,17,Fneed anything, are you okay, is there
OL,18,Fanything we can do to help you?' There
OL,19,Fwas nothing like that."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FClare said the impact of seeing her
OL,8,Fdad die in the way he did had a
OL,9,Fdevastating impact on her family and
OL,10,Fthey have "horrendous" memories of
OL,11,Fwhat happened.
OL,13,F"Instead of him slipping away
OL,14,Fpeacefully he died making a horrific,
OL,15,Fawful noise and we didn't understand
OL,16,Fwhat it was," she said. "My dad would
OL,17,Fbe devastated to know that we
OL,18,Fwitnessed that and how traumatised we
OL,19,Fwere."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
