PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe state of Wales' palliative care is
OL,8,Fa cause for concern for those at the
OL,9,FUK's leading end-of-life charity Marie
OL,10,FCurie, with figures showing demand for
OL,11,Fpalliative care is on the rise.
OL,13,FIt estimates that by the 2040s, 37,000
OL,14,Fpeople in Wales will need end of life
OL,15,Fcare each year.
OL,17,FFigures published by Marie Curie
OL,18,Fsuggest there are more than 10,000
OL,19,Fadults across Wales whose symptoms
OL,20,Faren't addressed, and who do not have
OL,21,Fenough support from their GP.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe organisation is calling for urgent
OL,8,Faction to transform support to ensure
OL,9,Fthose living with a terminal illness,
OL,10,Fboth now and in the future, can access
OL,11,Fthe care they need.
OL,13,FMarie Curie Cymru senior policy
OL,14,Fmanager Natasha Davies said: "It's
OL,15,Fsimply unacceptable that so many
OL,16,Fpeople are being left without the care
OL,17,Fand support they need at the end of
OL,18,Flife.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Too many people are spending their
OL,8,Fdays isolated, in pain and struggling
OL,9,Fto make ends meet. Carers are being
OL,10,Fleft abandoned without support, and
OL,11,Fservices and staff are struggling to
OL,12,Fdeliver the care people need, where
OL,13,Fand then they need it.
OL,15,F"Change is urgently needed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Transforming end-of-life care means
OL,8,Fmaking sure that everyone can access
OL,9,Fthe care they need in the right place,
OL,10,Fat the right time. It means taking a
OL,11,Fsystem-wide approach that fully
OL,12,Fintegrates palliative and end-of-life
OL,13,Fcare into health and social care, and
OL,14,Fensuring people have access to advice,
OL,15,Fsupport and care 24/7.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Placing palliative care nurses in
OL,8,Feach primary care cluster, integrating
OL,9,Fpalliative care paramedics into
OL,10,Fspecialist palliative care teams and
OL,11,Fproviding a 24/7 single point of
OL,12,Faccess for advice and information via
OL,13,F111, staffed by clinically trained
OL,14,Fpalliative care staff, would
OL,15,Fsignificantly improve access to
OL,16,Fservices and care coordination.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"We cannot afford to waste time
OL,8,Fgetting this right. The next Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment must show strong leadership
OL,10,Fand commit to the bold, radical
OL,11,Factions that are needed to truly
OL,12,Ftransform end of life care.
OL,14,F"People can add their voices to our
OL,15,Fcalls for change by signing our open
OL,16,Fletter, which will be sent to the
OL,17,FFirst Minister after May's election,
OL,18,Fand makes clear the need to turn warm
OL,19,Fwords into action."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FIn response to the situation, a Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment spokesperson said: "Good
OL,9,Fpalliative and end-of-life care can
OL,10,Fmake a huge difference to those with
OL,11,Flife-limiting illness, helping them to
OL,12,Fdie with dignity, and help the
OL,13,Fgrieving process for those left behind.
OL,15,F"We provide more than #16m a year to
OL,16,Fmake sure everyone has access to the
OL,17,Fbest possible end-of-life care. This
OL,18,Fincludes offering a suite of advance
OL,19,Fand future care planning resources for
OL,20,Fthe public and for health and social
OL,21,Fcare professionals.
OL,26,@pD@_OUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
