PN,46613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772917925
OL,3,CWoman 'traumatised' watching her
OL,4,Cfather die with 'lack' of palliative
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Work on a new hospice commissioning
OL,8,Fapproach is ongoing to ensure fair
OL,9,Faccess, long-term sustainability, and
OL,10,Fhigh-quality care across Wales."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]
